*** Patch Proposal v1.0 ***
This is a *proposal* patch. It assumes:
- sdd-templates/tools/speckit_lint.py exists and has validate_feature(feature_path)
- Gate approvals are tracked in specs/<feature>/APPROVAL.md (human-only)
- Coverage tier is defined in basic_design.md YAML as coverage_tier

